metadata.description:
Shoguns is a project composed of 500 items aiming to develop the NFT art community. Each NFT shogun gives you a unique private key, giving you access to our monthly giveaways and community space. 

Each key is equivalent to a temporary right to participate in the giveaways and to an exclusive role in the community space offering you benefits !

There are 2 categories of keys representing a duration: 6 or 12 months. The number of months included on your key equals the number of your future available participations. The rarest shoguns offer you the more durable keys, the best roles and more chances to win the rewards offered such as nitro discord, money, or other exclusive NFTs. The bigger the community, the bigger the rewards. 


Our goal is to create a space where people can speak freely about NFT art, the contest is there to make it grow.

After purchasing your first shogun, click on the following link: https://discord.gg/Bbv2adrn3b and follow the instructions. Enjoy!
